#

Braised Beef Short Ribs with Creamy Mashed Cassava

195 min
$25
700 kcal
Difficulty: 30%
Servings: 4

Allergens:

Dairy

Dietary Tags:

Gluten-FreeDairy

Cuisine:

AmericanComfort Food

Course:

Main Dish

Tags:

Comfort FoodHearty MealSlow Cooked

Description

Tender beef short ribs braised to perfection, served with creamy and buttery mashed cassava for a deliciously comforting meal.

Ingredients

  • beef short ribs: 2 lbs
  • onion: 1, chopped
  • garlic: 4 cloves, minced
  • beef broth: 4 cups
  • red wine: 1 cup
  • tomato paste: 2 tbsp
  • thyme: 1 tsp
  • bay leaves: 2
  • salt: to taste
  • black pepper: to taste
  • cassava: 1.5 lbs
  • butter: 4 tbsp
  • milk: 1/2 cup
